      sideEffects: "Hepatotoxicity, orange-red discoloration of body fluids (urine, tears, sweat, saliva), GI upset, thrombocytopenia, flu-like syndrome",
      contra: "Concurrent use with protease inhibitors or many other medications (potent CYP450 inducer with extensive drug interactions); active hepatitis; hypersensitivity",
